* {{ill|Sai Binrō|ja|狭井檳榔}} – A general in the Battle of Baekgang.
* {{ill|Luhara Omi|ja|廬原臣}} – A general in the Battle of Baekgang.
* {{ill|Kawabe Momoe|ja|河辺百枝}} – A general who survived the Battle of Baekgang.
